				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\text{NO}}^{ - }_{2} $$\end{document}) [55], while sulphates may undergo reduction to form H2S and H2O [50].

